Movie Ticket Booking System
-----------------------------------------

Almost similer to book my show.

Features
---------------
1. User can create their account and login
2. User can be able to search movie(City wise, Threatre wise, show timewise)
3. User can book a seat in particular show
4. User can checkout and pay the booking fees
5. User will be notified when the booking is confirmed
6. User will get discount
    a. on Friday afternoon shows
    b. If user has booked 3 tickets, he will get 50% off on the 3rd ticket

Apply all the knowledge from the sessions.

Eureka
Router
User
Threatre
checkout
discount
